RawQuestion: which city held the summer olympics twice?
ProcessedQuestion: which city held the summer olympics twice

Parses.Sparql:
#MANUAL SPARQL
PREFIX ns: <http://rdf.freebase.com/ns/>
SELECT DISTINCT  ?city 
WHERE {
  ns:m.06vvk ns:time.recurring_event.instances ?y . # Summer Olympic Games
  ?y ns:olympics.olympic_games.host_city ?city .
}
GROUP BY ?city
Having COUNT(?city) = 2
